scene_description_enriched: Two haloed women are depicted in a landscape setting with two stylized trees. The woman on the left, dressed in a pale garment and an orange robe, has her hand on her abdomen. The woman on the right, wearing an orange robe and a white head covering, is leaning towards the first woman and touching her abdomen. The background is a textured gold, suggesting a divine or elevated space, with green ground and trees indicating an outdoor setting.
